name: Test Chamber (Darako)
description:
CXFAI = SixFive

here i do my stupid science

AWSD - Movement
Space - Jump
Ctrl - Crouch
R - Restart
C - Zoom In
Z - Zoom Out
E - Interact
Left Click - Grab
Right Click - Yeet (when grabbing)

there are also other keybinds to do dumb shit but you need to figure them out
